<br>
Back in the day when every mob had 32k hp max, wizards were viewed as Uber.  So Verant nerfed our lure line of spells so they now have more resists.  Other casters could touch most of these mobs also in Kunark and the old world.  Hence all casters contributed greatly to their group. Even with the Lure nerfs we usually outshined other casters.  <br>
<br>
Then along came Velious, verant decided they would get rid of the 32k hp barrier. Not only for Velious but also the planes and probably more to come also.  With the new weapons that do excellent damage and no implement of better spells ALL casters became less effective.  So the question is why did the Wizard class hurt the most?  The other casters have alternative way to hurt the mobs, pets, damage shields, ect.  All casters hurt from the changes, but Wizards hurt the most.<br>
<br>
So now we come to two paths in the road for Verant to take.  One they can balance all the classes or revert all mobs Hp's back to 32k max.  They decide to balance the classes, when doing this they add excellent additions very needed to many classes.  But they do not enhance the spell damage for ANY classes or possible damage in one bar of mana for ANY caster.  <br>
<br>
This is where we stand now on the path of Everquest.  A diminished need for casters in general.  A greatly diminished need for non-support classes.  It is not on purpose, but just a coincedence that our class hurt the most from this change.<br>
<br>
Future outlooks:  Verant could either give all casters upgrades to damage mobs with, or they could lower all mobs Hp's back down to the 32k hp mark.  As for online games go, if they continue on this path of raising the bar with no caster enchancements EQ will soon fade away as more and more casters flee to other games from lack of support. (not just wizards)  <br>
<br>
Or they could be smart and just lower the Hp max back down to 32k and make the mobs tougher.  Then all classes would be balanced once again.  As it stands right now they can NOT enhance ANY caster without them walking through old world and Kunark mobs.  Hehe, uber guilds do right now.<br>
<br>
My point: If they continue on this road of upping the Hp and difficulty of mobs, they must enhance ALL casters to make of for this. And you will see All casters flee to another game. If they lower the Hp cap back down to 32k then they resolved all their problems at once.    <br>
<br>
Now just to sit back and see what they do...<br>
